Abezimo eziphuthumayo babizelwe eMontclair, eningizimu neTheku, ebusuku ngo-10 ngemva kwemibiko yokuthi kunowesilisa ogwaziwe. Bafike kule ndawo bathola owesilisa oneminyaka ewu-30 ubudala esesimweni esibucayi ngenxa yokulimala kabi. “Lo mlisa ulashelwe endaweni yesigameko ngaphambi kokuphuthunyiswa esibhedlela,” kuchaza uKyle Van Reenen we-Emer-G Med. Amaphoyisa aseMontclair asaphenya. 